---
/**
 * /artifacts — DEPRECATED (308 redirect to /locker#artifacts).
 *
 * Per SITE-ARCHITECTURE.md, the evidence drawer becomes a section of
 * the Regular File hub at /locker. The hash anchor #artifacts lands
 * the visitor at the new Evidence Drawer section. The previous
 * <ArtifactGrid> mount now lives in /locker.astro.
 *
 * Astro emits the fragment in the Location header; browsers honor it
 * by jumping to the matching id on the destination page.
 */
return Astro.redirect('/locker#artifacts', 308);
